name":"Skincare","@type":"SiteNavigationElement","position":2,"description":"Shop skincare products at Sephora. Find top-rated products from leading skincare brands to help target specific skin concerns and revitalize your look."},{"url":"https://www.sephora.com/ca/en/shop/hair-products","name":"Hair","@type":"SiteNavigationElement","position":3,"description":"Explore our top-rated hair care products at Sephora. Browse an unrivaled selection of shampoos, conditioners, styling products, hair color and more from top brands."},{"url":"https://www.sephora.com/ca/en/shop/fragrance","name":"Fragrance","@type":"SiteNavigationElement","position":4,"description":"Shop fragrances for women and men at Sephora. Find your favorite perfume or cologne or accentuate your style with a new scent."},{"url":"https://www.sephora.com/ca/en/shop/makeup-tools","name":"Tools & Brushes","@type":"SiteNavigationElement","position":5,"description":"Shop beauty tools and accessories at Sephora. Find top-rated makeup tools, brushes, applicators, spa tools and more from leading brands."},{"url":"https://www.sephora.com/ca/en/shop/bath-body","name":"Bath & Body","@type":"SiteNavigationElement","position":6,"description":"Shop bath & body products at Sephora. Find an unrivaled selection of the top moisturizers, cleansers, lotions, exfoliants, scrubs and more from top brands."},{"url":"https://www.sephora.com/ca/en/sale","name":"Sale","@type":"SiteNavigationElement","position":7,"description":"Makeup sales are always on at Sephora. Shop discounted makeup, skincare, fragrance and hair care products at Sephora today. Free shipping and samples available."}]}</script><script type="application/ld+json">{"itemListElement":[{"item":{"name":"Fragrance","@id":"https://www.sephora.com/ca/en/shop/fragrance"},"@type":"ListItem","position":1},{"item":{"name":"Women","@id":"https://www.sephora.com/ca/en/shop/fragrances-for-women"},"@type":"ListItem","position":2},{"item":{"name":"Perfume","@id":"https://www.sephora.com/ca/en/shop/perfume"},"@type":"ListItem","position":3}],"@type":"BreadcrumbList","@context":"http://schema.org"}</script><script type="application/ld+json">{"@type":"ProductGroup","@context":"http://schema.org","name":"Black Phantom Eau de Parfum with Coffee & Sandalwood","description":"Shop Black Phantom by Kilian at Sephora. This fragrance contains notes of rum, coffee, and sandalwood.","brand":{"@type":"Brand","name":"KILIAN Paris"},"image":"https://www.sephora.com/productimages/sku/s2320174-main-hero.jpg","@id":"https://www.sephora.com/ca/en/product/black-phantom-memento-mori-P429627","url":"https://www.sephora.com/ca/en/product/black-phantom-memento-mori-P429627","productGroupID":"P429627","category":"perfume","hasVariant":[{"@type":"Product","name":"Black Phantom Eau de Parfum with Coffee & Sandalwood","sku":"2320174","image":"https://www.sephora.com/productimages/sku/s2320174-main-hero.jpg","offers":{"@type":"Offer","price":"385.0","priceCurrency":"CAD","availability":"https://schema.org/InStock","seller":{"@type":"Organization","name":"Sephora"}}}],"aggregateRating":{"reviewCount":"163","bestRating":"5","ratingValue":"4.245398773006135","itemReviewed":{"name":null}},"reviews":[{"datePublished":"2025-09-30","@type":"Review","author":{"name":"klarajeon"},"name":null,"description":"This is the best perfume ever! I never blind buy any perfumes especially if it’s as expensive as this one. And to be clear I have a very particular taste in perfumes and have never found my signature scent but this perfume is something else. As soon as I sprayed it I knew it was the one and it will be a forever repurchase!!!","itemReviewed":{"name":null},"@id":"360909559","reviewRating":{"bestRating":"5","ratingValue":"5"}},{"datePublished":"2025-03-04","@type":"Review","author":{"name":"FlightMama"},"name":"Beautiful, smells so good!","description":"Love love love this perfume. I can see how it’s not for everyone, its smell is very unique. To me it smells warm, nutty, a dark gourmand and is perfect for fall/winter. It’s definitely unisex, my son and I both wear it well. Try before you buy, but this is my favorite","itemReviewed":{"name":null},"@id":"339472642","reviewRating":{"bestRating":"5","ratingValue":"5"}},{"datePublished":"2025-01-03","@type":"Review","author":{"name":"FAME93"},"name":"Awful","description":"Do not get this. Just go with angel share fellas.","itemReviewed":{"name":null},"@id":"331010452","reviewRating":{"bestRating":"5","ratingValue":"1"}},{"datePublished":"2024-08-13","@type":"Review","author":{"name":"sarbear22"},"name":"It’s Giving… Wood","description":"This perfume is very unique which I find refreshing as many perfumery’s seem to carry the same one note fragrance but just slap a new label on the bottle. This perfume is incredibly woody. It leans a little too woody for my liking. I adore sandalwood but it goes unbalanced without a note that can either balance it. It’s not leaning clean or sweet- just woody. For the price of this perfume, I expected to be blown away with something well balanced and wearable. Sadly I think this truly is a collectors fragrance and would satisfy a small niche of buyers.","itemReviewed":{"name":null},"@id":"316595742","reviewRating":{"bestRating":"5","ratingValue":"2"}},{"datePublished":"2024-08-11","@type":"Review","author":{"name":"krisfek"},"name":"Not for me unfortunately","description":"I was so excited to try out Sacred Wood by Kilian. As in really excited. But all I can say is I’m not impressed. It smells awful in my opinion. I don’t know what’s happening. It’s a strong scent and I gravitate towards strong scents but this is not for me. It’s way too serious and old. Not light, or fun or pretty. It would be better as a candle in my opinion.","itemReviewed":{"name":null},"@id":"316376781","reviewRating":{"bestRating":"5","ratingValue":"3"}},{"datePublished":"2024-06-24","@type":"Review","author":{"name":"licensedtolove"},"name":"Rich and deep","description":"This is rich, deep, and masculine leaning. When I initially received I was on the fence but now that it has sat for a few months it is super intoxicating! Glad I held onto it.","itemReviewed":{"name":null},"@id":"312706064","reviewRating":{"bestRating":"5","ratingValue":"4"}},{"datePublished":"2024-06-11","@type":"Review","author":{"name":"macademia"},"name":"Must try","description":"Phenomenal scent. Warm, coffee and chocolate is definitely pronounced on my skin and in the end it goes into skin musk. Love this scent and I find it original and exquisite. I would recommend a sample as it is a dark scent, definitely gourmand so you need to be a lover of that. On my skin is smells perfectly unisex, but some other women might find it masculin. I find it intoxicating. I definitely smell pronounced coffee and dark chocolate on me. Rum just after spraying, but I would not call this perfume boozy. Definitely not as Angel's Share( which I love too). After few hours tonka and praline comes, and after about 8 hours I smell musk. Delicious fragrance.","itemReviewed":{"name":null},"@id":"311569330","reviewRating":{"bestRating":"5","ratingValue":"5"}},{"datePublished":"2024-05-19","@type":"Review","author":{"name":"Fragluv"},"name":"Lovely Gourmand","description":"Black Phantom by Kilian is an exquisite fragrance—luxurious, deep, and mysterious. However, its high price tag is hard to justify. For the same enchanting experience at a fraction of the cost, try \"Casper\" by Klone Fragrances. It’s the exact same. You won’t be disappointed!","itemReviewed":{"name":null},"@id":"309791640","reviewRating":{"bestRating":"5","ratingValue":"5"}},{"datePublished":"2024-03-25","@type":"Review","author":{"name":"julesmeows"},"name":"AMAZING!!!","description":"OMG. This is my absolute favourite cologne on my boyfriend. Whenever he wears it, I instantly fall in love again and again!! Best he's ever worn! I could eat him up","itemReviewed":{"name":null},"@id":"275107041","reviewRating":{"bestRating":"5","ratingValue":"5"}},{"datePublished":"2023-12-28","@type":"Review","author":{"name":"karenoreilly"},"name":"Gorgeous fragrance!","description":"One of my all time favourites! I always get tons of compliments from everyone when I wear this! Even young children, tell me how much they love it! It’s slightly sweet, warm & spicy, sexy and  luxurious","itemReviewed":{"name":null},"@id":"267307787","reviewRating":{"bestRating":"5","ratingValue":"5"}}]}</script></main></div><div rootid="ErrorBoundary(ReduxProvider(EmotionGlobalProvider(AfterEventsRendering(Connect(Footer)))))" style="display:contents"><style data-emotion="css-global 149d46d">:root{--color-black:#000;--color-white:#fff;--color-lightRed:#FCECEC;--color-red:#cf112c;--color-brightRed:#e2030f;--color-green:#008048;--color-yellow:#ffc003;--color-blue:#136BEA;--color-lightBlue:#e5f2fd;--color-gray:#666;--color-darkGray:#3F3F3F;--color-inputGray:#888;--color-midGray:#ccc;--color-lightGray:#eee;--color-nearWhite:#f6f6f8;--color-babyPink:#f4b6c7;--color-paleTurquoise:#b2fce4;--color-goldenYellow:#f8d15d;--color-venmoBlue:#008cff;--color-venmoLightBlue:#299EFF;--color-pazeBlue:#0F42F8;--color-orange:#FFB761;--color-darken1:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.0625);--color-darken2:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125);--color-darken3:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);--color-error:#cf112c;--color-base:#000;--color-link:#136BEA;--color-divider:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.0625);--font-family-base:"helvetica neue",helvetica,arial,sans-serif;--font-family-serif:georgia,times,serif;--font-size-xs:11px;--font-size-sm:12px;--font-size-base:14px;--font-size-md:16px;--font-size-lg:20px;--font-size-xl:24px;--font-size-2xl:32px;--font-size-3xl:48px;--font-size-xs-bg:11px;--font-size-sm-bg:12px;--font-size-base-bg:14px;--font-size-md-bg:16px;--font-size-lg-bg:18px;--font-size-xl-bg:20px;--font-size-2xl-bg:24px;--font-size-3xl-bg:26px;--font-size-4xl-bg:36px;--font-weight-light:300;--font-weight-normal:400;--font-weight-medium:500;--font-weight-demiBold:600;--font-weight-bold:700;--leading-none:1;--leadin