talize your look.\"},{\"url\":\"https://www.sephora.com/ca/en/shop/hair-products\",\"name\":\"Hair\",\"@type\":\"SiteNavigationElement\",\"position\":3,\"description\":\"Explore our top-rated hair care products at Sephora. Browse an unrivaled selection of shampoos, conditioners, styling products, hair color and more from top brands.\"},{\"url\":\"https://www.sephora.com/ca/en/shop/fragrance\",\"name\":\"Fragrance\",\"@type\":\"SiteNavigationElement\",\"position\":4,\"description\":\"Shop fragrances for women and men at Sephora. Find your favorite perfume or cologne or accentuate your style with a new scent.\"},{\"url\":\"https://www.sephora.com/ca/en/shop/makeup-tools\",\"name\":\"Tools & Brushes\",\"@type\":\"SiteNavigationElement\",\"position\":5,\"description\":\"Shop beauty tools and accessories at Sephora. Find top-rated makeup tools, brushes, applicators, spa tools and more from leading brands.\"},{\"url\":\"https://www.sephora.com/ca/en/shop/bath-body\",\"name\":\"Bath & Body\",\"@type\":\"SiteNavigationElement\",\"position\":6,\"description\":\"Shop bath & body products at Sephora. Find an unrivaled selection of the top moisturizers, cleansers, lotions, exfoliants, scrubs and more from top brands.\"},{\"url\":\"https://www.sephora.com/ca/en/sale\",\"name\":\"Sale\",\"@type\":\"SiteNavigationElement\",\"position\":7,\"description\":\"Makeup sales are always on at Sephora. Shop discounted makeup, skincare, fragrance and hair care products at Sephora today. Free shipping and samples available.\"}]}","productSeoJsonLd":"{\"@type\":\"ProductGroup\",\"@context\":\"http://schema.org\",\"name\":\"Black Phantom Eau de Parfum with Coffee & Sandalwood\",\"description\":\"Shop Black Phantom by Kilian at Sephora. This fragrance contains notes of rum, coffee, and sandalwood.\",\"brand\":{\"@type\":\"Brand\",\"name\":\"KILIAN Paris\"},\"image\":\"https://www.sephora.com/productimages/sku/s2320174-main-hero.jpg\",\"@id\":\"https://www.sephora.com/ca/en/product/black-phantom-memento-mori-P429627\",\"url\":\"https://www.sephora.com/ca/en/product/black-phantom-memento-mori-P429627\",\"productGroupID\":\"P429627\",\"category\":\"perfume\",\"hasVariant\":[{\"@type\":\"Product\",\"name\":\"Black Phantom Eau de Parfum with Coffee & Sandalwood\",\"sku\":\"2320174\",\"image\":\"https://www.sephora.com/productimages/sku/s2320174-main-hero.jpg\",\"offers\":{\"@type\":\"Offer\",\"price\":\"385.0\",\"priceCurrency\":\"CAD\",\"availability\":\"https://schema.org/InStock\",\"seller\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Sephora\"}}}],\"aggregateRating\":{\"reviewCount\":\"163\",\"bestRating\":\"5\",\"ratingValue\":\"4.245398773006135\",\"itemReviewed\":{\"name\":null}},\"reviews\":[{\"datePublished\":\"2025-09-30\",\"@type\":\"Review\",\"author\":{\"name\":\"klarajeon\"},\"name\":null,\"description\":\"This is the best perfume ever! I never blind buy any perfumes especially if it’s as expensive as this one. And to be clear I have a very particular taste in perfumes and have never found my signature scent but this perfume is something else. As soon as I sprayed it I knew it was the one and it will be a forever repurchase!!!\",\"itemReviewed\":{\"name\":null},\"@id\":\"360909559\",\"reviewRating\":{\"bestRating\":\"5\",\"ratingValue\":\"5\"}},{\"datePublished\":\"2025-03-04\",\"@type\":\"Review\",\"author\":{\"name\":\"FlightMama\"},\"name\":\"Beautiful, smells so good!\",\"description\":\"Love love love this perfume. I can see how it’s not for everyone, its smell is very unique. To me it smells warm, nutty, a dark gourmand and is perfect for fall/winter. It’s definitely unisex, my son and I both wear it well. Try before you buy, but this is my favorite\",\"itemReviewed\":{\"name\":null},\"@id\":\"339472642\",\"reviewRating\":{\"bestRating\":\"5\",\"ratingValue\":\"5\"}},{\"datePublished\":\"2025-01-03\",\"@type\":\"Review\",\"author\":{\"name\":\"FAME93\"},\"name\":\"Awful\",\"description\":\"Do not get this. Just go with angel share fellas.\",\"itemReviewed\":{\"name\":null},\"@id\":\"331010452\",\"reviewRating\":{\"bestRating\":\"5\",\"ratingValue\":\"1\"}},{\"datePublished\":\"2024-08-13\",\"@type\":\"Review\",\"author\":{\"name\":\"sarbear22\"},\"name\":\"It’s Giving… Wood\",\"description\":\"This perfume is very unique which I find refreshing as many perfumery’s seem to carry the same one note fragrance but just slap a new label on the bottle. This perfume is incredibly woody. It leans a little too woody for my liking. I adore sandalwood but it goes unbalanced without a note that can either balance it. It’s not leaning clean or sweet- just woody. For the price of this perfume, I expected to be blown away with something well balanced and wearable. Sadly I think this truly is a collectors fragrance and would satisfy a small niche of buyers.\",\"itemReviewed\":{\"name\":null},\"@id\":\"316595742\",\"reviewRating\":{\"bestRating\":\"5\",\"ratingValue\":\"2\"}},{\"datePublished\":\"2024-08-11\",\"@type\":\"Review\",\"author\":{\"name\":\"krisfek\"},\"name\":\"Not for me unfortunately\",\"description\":\"I was so excited to try out Sacred Wood by Kilian. As in really excited. But all I can say is I’m not impressed. It smells awful in my opinion. I don’t know what’s happening. It’s a strong scent and I gravitate towards strong scents but this is not for me. It’s way too serious and old. Not light, or fun or pretty. It would be better as a candle in my opinion.\",\"itemReviewed\":{\"name\":null},\"@id\":\"316376781\",\"reviewRating\":{\"bestRating\":\"5\",\"ratingValue\":\"3\"}},{\"datePublished\":\"2024-06-24\",\"@type\":\"Review\",\"author\":{\"name\":\"licensedtolove\"},\"name\":\"Rich and deep\",\"description\":\"This is rich, deep, and masculine leaning. When I initially received I was on the fence but now that it has sat for a few months it is super intoxicating! Glad I held onto it.\",\"itemReviewed\":{\"name\":null},\"@id\":\"312706064\",\"reviewRating\":{\"bestRating\":\"5\",\"ratingValue\":\"4\"}},{\"datePublished\":\"2024-06-11\",\"@type\":\"Review\",\"author\":{\"name\":\"macademia\"},\"name\":\"Must try\",\"description\":\"Phenomenal scent. Warm, coffee and chocolate is definitely pronounced on my skin and in the end it goes into skin musk. Love this scent and I find it original and exquisite. I would recommend a sample as it is a dark scent, definitely gourmand so you need to be a lover of that. On my skin is smells perfectly unisex, but some other women might find it masculin. I find it intoxicating. I definitely smell pronounced coffee and dark chocolate on me. Rum just after spraying, but I would not call this perfume boozy. Definitely not as Angel's Share( which I love too). After few hours tonka and praline comes, and after about 8 hours I smell musk. Delicious fragrance.\",\"itemReviewed\":{\"name\":null},\"@id\":\"311569330\",\"reviewRating\":{\"bestRating\":\"5\",\"ratingValue\":\"5\"}},{\"datePublished\":\"2024-05-19\",\"@type\":\"Review\",\"author\":{\"name\":\"Fragluv\"},\"name\":\"Lovely Gourmand\",\"description\":\"Black Phantom by Kilian is an exquisite fragrance—luxurious, deep, and mysterious. However, its high price tag is hard to justify. For the same enchanting experience at a fraction of the cost, try \\\"Casper\\\" by Klone Fragrances. It’s the exact same. You won’t be disappointed!\",\"itemReviewed\":{\"name\":null},\"@id\":\"309791640\",\"reviewRating\":{\"bestRating\":\"5\",\"ratingValue\":\"5\"}},{\"datePublished\":\"2024-03-25\",\"@type\":\"Review\",\"author\":{\"name\":\"julesmeows\"},\"name\":\"AMAZING!!!\",\"description\":\"OMG. This is my absolute favourite cologne on my boyfriend. Whenever he wears it, I instantly fall in love again and again!! Best he's ever worn! I could eat him up\",\"itemReviewed\":{\"name\":null},\"@id\":\"275107041\",\"reviewRating\":{\"bestRating\":\"5\",\"ratingValue\":\"5\"}},{\"datePublished\":\"2023-12-28\",\"@type\":\"Review\",\"author\":{\"name\":\"karenoreilly\"},\"name\":\"Gorgeous fragrance!\",\"description\":\"One of my all time favourites! I always get tons of compliments from everyone when I wear this! Even young children, tell me how much they love it! It’s slightly sweet, warm & spicy, sexy and  luxurious\",\"itemReviewed\":{\"name\":null},\"@id\":\"267307787\",\"reviewRating\":{\"bestRating\":\"5\",\"ratingValue\":\"5\"}}]}","linkEquityBlock":{"links":[{"url":"https://www.sephora.com/ca/en/shop/perfume","anchorText":"Perfume & Perfumes for Women"},{"url":"https://www.sephora.com/ca/en/shop/hair-products","anchorText":"Hair Care Products"},{"url":"https://www.sephora.com/ca/en/shop/gifts","anchorText":"Best Beauty Gifts in 2026"},{"url":"https://www.sephora.com/ca/en/shop/face-mask","anchorText":"Face Masks | Facial Masks"},{"url":"https://www.sephora.com/ca/en/shop/shampoo-sulfate-free-shampoo","anchorText":"Shampoo, Sulfate Free Shampoo & Clarifying Shampoo"},{"url":"https://www.sephora.com/ca/en/shop/fake-eyelashes-false-eyelashes","anchorText":"Fake Eyelashes"},{"url":"https://www.sephora.com/ca/en/shop/moisturizer-skincare","anchorText":"Moisturizer, Face Moisturizer & Skin Moisturizer"},{"url":"https://www.sephora.com/ca/en/shop/sheet-masks","anchorText":"Sheet Masks"},{"url":"https://www.sephora.com/ca/en/shop/diffusers","anchorText":"Diffusers | Essential Oil Diffusers"}]},"relatedLinks":[{"name":"Red Bottle Perfume","url":"/buy/red-bottle-perfume"},{"name":"Timeless Perfume","url":"/buy/timeless-perfume"},{"name":"Perfumes In Black Bottles","url":"/buy/perfumes-in-black-bottles"},{"name":"Black Bottle Colognes","url":"/buy/black-bottle-colognes"},{"name":"Blackberry Perfume","url":"/buy/blackberry-perfume"},{"name":"Dark Fragrance","url":"/buy/dark-fragrance"},{"name":"Black Currant Perfume","url":"/buy/black-currant-perfume"},{"name":"Night Perfume","url":"/buy/night-perfume"},{"name":"Quality Perfume","url":"/buy/quality-perfume"},{"name":"Strong Perfume Oil","url":"/buy/strong-perfume-oil"}],"reviewFilters":[{"id":"sort","bvName":"sort","la